sequenceDiagram
    actor 用户
    participant CLI as CLI/WebUI
    participant CFG as config.py
    participant WL as wordlist.py
    participant SC as scanner.py
    participant CL as classifier.py
    participant NET as 目标网站
    participant RPT as report.py

    用户->>CLI: 输入参数 / 提交表单
    CLI->>CFG: load_settings()
    CFG-->>CLI: 返回默认配置
    CLI->>WL: read_wordlist(file, exts)
    WL-->>CLI: 返回路径列表 [paths]
    CLI->>SC: WebScanner(url, paths, threads)
    loop 每个路径 (多线程)
        SC->>NET: HTTP GET /path
        NET-->>SC: 响应（状态码, 响应体）
        SC->>CL: check_risk(path)
        CL-->>SC: (risk_type, risk_level)
        SC->>SC: 构建 ScanResult
    end
    SC-->>CLI: 返回 results[]
    CLI->>RPT: save_html_report(results)
    RPT-->>用户: 生成 report.html
